						<div class="postbody">If updating iNES, how could we describe more precisely the ammount of PRG/CHR ROM? iNES defines PRG in 16KB pages, but there should be support for smaller ROM's, no? Are those games even compatible with older emulators, or do their ROM files contain duplicated data to fill the necessary 16KB?
<br />
<br />I think board names stored in text format are useless, especialy when we have only 8 bytes left to implement new stuff. Codes would be just fine.</div>

