						<div class="postbody">Yeah, it's ugly, but it's flexible.  Would allow for some pretty neat stuff too while still retaining backwards compatability:
<br /><ul>Game name<br />Game description<br />Box images<br />Checksum (to check file integrity, not for game identification/'fixes')<br />...<br /></ul>
<br />
<br />Admittadly, this is all fluff, and I'm sure many would be opposed to having such 'useless' info attached to the rom, but I would certainly like to have it.  Heck, make it something like (buzzword alert) XML, and it can have as much or as little info as you want it to have.</div>

					
